version_description: The other sheet has got many mistakes and is very inaccurate. This one should be correct and complete.
This version is closer to the original

My version is in a different key, which provides another way to play it, and it is cleaned up more than the others, as well as it also has better clarification on the individual verses and choruses in the song.

I sent this tab again because, though other versions sound good, they seemed to me more difficult and/or confusing. There were some minor mistakes in other versions so I tried to chord this song with corrections and instead with simple chords for beginners.

song_name: Gloriaangels We Have Heard On High
